China Camp

Clean environment and read in data

Convert to date

cc$date<-as.POSIXct(cc$DateTimeStamp, format = c("%m/%d/%Y %H:%M"))

Calculate weekly salinity average and sd

cc$week_year<-date2week(cc$date, floor_day=TRUE)
sal_week_av<-aggregate( Sal ~ week_year,cc, mean)
sal_week_sd<-aggregate(Sal~week_year,cc, sd)

Change column names

names(sal_week_av)[names(sal_week_av) == "Sal"] <- "week_sal_av"
names(sal_week_sd)[names(sal_week_sd) == "Sal"] <- "week_sal_sd"

Combine data frames

cc_sal_summary<-cbind(sal_week_av, sal_week_sd)

Add the monthly average and sd columns to the eos df

cc_new<-merge(cc, cc_sal_summary[, c("week_year", "week_sal_av", "week_sal_sd")], by="week_year")

Caluculate 3 standard deviations from monthly average and then remove salinity values that are greater.

cc_new$remove<-(3*cc_new$week_sal_sd)+cc_new$week_sal_av
removed_data<-filter(cc_new, Sal<=remove)

Graph to compare data sets

removed<-ggplot(data = removed_data, mapping = aes(x = date, y = Sal, color=Sal)) + geom_point()  +stat_smooth(colour="green")+ggtitle("Outliers Removed") +  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 12, face = "plain")) +theme(axis.text=element_text(size=12),axis.title=element_text(size=12,face="plain")) + ylab("Salinity") + xlab("") + theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(), panel.background = element_blank(), axis.line = element_line(colour = "black"))

all<-ggplot(data = cc, mapping = aes(x = date, y = Sal, color=Sal)) + geom_point()  +stat_smooth(colour="green")+ggtitle("Raw Data")+  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 12, face = "plain")) +theme(axis.text=element_text(size=12),axis.title=element_text(size=12,face="plain")) + ylab("Salinity") + xlab("") + theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(), panel.background = element_blank(), axis.line = element_line(colour = "black"))

ggarrange(all, removed, ncol=2, nrow=1)

test <- cc_salinity[!(cc_salinity$Sal < 4.8 & cc_salinity$month_yr=="2017-05") &
    !(cc_salinity$Sal < 4.8 & cc_salinity$month_yr=="2017-06")&                  !(cc_salinity$Sal < 4.8 & cc_salinity$month_yr=="2017-04")&
